<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Health Link</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #D3D3D3;
            color: #2C2C2C;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            padding-top: 80px; /* Space for the fixed header */
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            position: fixed;
            top: 10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 95%;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #6A5ACD;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        nav li {
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        nav li:last-child {
            margin-right: 0;
        }

        nav a {
            position: relative;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007BFF;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 0;
        }

        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 5px;
            right: 0;
            background: #007BFF;
            transition: width 0.4s ease;
        }

        nav a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
            left: 0;
            background: #0056b3;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        .section-1 {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            width: 90%;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            top: 60px;
        }

        .section-1 h1 {
            color: #6A5ACD;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section-1 p {
            color: #2C2C2C;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Health Link</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Viruses</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">More Viruses</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Learn to Isolate</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Use AI to Diagnose</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Sign Up/Log in</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="section-1">
        <h1>Welcome to Health Link</h1>
        <p>Health Link is a website that provides information about viruses and how to isolate yourself if you are infected. We also provide a tool that uses AI to help diagnose your symptoms. Whether you are a doctor or a normal civilian, this website is for you!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
